<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 01:06:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着伊朗冲突持续，加密货币市场追踪战争风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/crypto-markets-track-war-risk-as-iran-conflict-endures</link><description>加密货币市场再次成为交易者如何定价中东持续冲突的唯一开放窗口，随着伊朗战争进入第二周，Hyperliquid 上跟踪石油、黄金和白银的合约显示出显着的走势。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0qzdRvR17UY/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 14:32:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/crypto-markets-track-war-risk-as-iran-conflict-endures</guid></item><item><title>稳定币公司在几乎不存在的人工智能代理支付上押下重注</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/stablecoin-firms-bet-big-on-ai-agent-payments-that-barely-exist</link><description>Circle Internet Group Inc. 和 Stripe Inc. 正在竞相为一个尚不存在的世界构建支付系统——在这个世界中，自主人工智能代理每天进行数百万次交易，以稳定币结算，而不是刷信用卡。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJiLirZFi0gc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-07/stablecoin-firms-bet-big-on-ai-agent-payments-that-barely-exist</guid></item><item><title>随着交易员评估伊朗的波动性，比特币小幅下跌</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-btc-edges-downward-as-traders-take-stock-of-iran-volatility</link><description>随着投资者消化美国经济数据的发布并应对中东的事态发展，比特币跌破 68,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igIKnsTrADrc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 11:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-btc-edges-downward-as-traders-take-stock-of-iran-volatility</guid></item><item><title>随着波动性的回归，比特币与股票的相关性飙升</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-s-correlation-with-stocks-surges-as-volatility-returns</link><description>比特币再次与美国股市密切同步，这对加密货币顽固分子来说几乎是最糟糕的时刻。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOpaLmZrsPf8/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 20:35:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-s-correlation-with-stocks-surges-as-volatility-returns</guid></item></channel></rss>